1.1.0:
- First really usable version.
- Added: support for update requests - use Xa to get new packages.
- Added: support for restart requests (to call after an update
  to take it into account)

1.1.1:
- Fixed: daemonization option should not be available under Windows.

1.1.2:
- Fixed: large payloads over Xa are now correctly sent.
- Modified: now use cPickle instead of pickle.
- Fixed: some error conditions in tcp and sctp probes.
